                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "question",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p>WLP-1 is designed to activate your body's natural GLP-1 response — the same hormone targeted by medications like Ozempic and Wegovy. It helps you burn more calories at rest and feel full faster. Berberine works differently: it targets blood sugar regulation and insulin sensitivity, which directly impacts cravings and energy stability. They complement each other well — which is why we bundle them in the Ultimate Stack.</p>",
